thread.title: Football roundups for Oct. 9, 2015

author: ASHLEY SQUIRES
title: Football roundups for Oct. 9, 2015
text:
ARToberFEST brings vivid color to downtown Galveston 
The Grand 1894 Opera House is hosting its 18th Annual ARToberFEST from 10 a.m. to 6 p.m. Saturday, Oct. 17 and from 10 a.m. to 5 p.m. Sunday, Oct. 18. The festival will be held on Postoffice Street between 21st and 23 Streets. Recognizing volunteer firefighters 
One source of hometown heroes in our community is our volunteer fire department. To recognize some of those hometown heroes, our city volunteer fire department hosted its annual awards banquet Sept. 29 at Fire Station No. 2. District Chief Daniel Gibbs said, “We want to recognize the firefighters who go above and beyond and continuously demonstrate excellence throughout the year.”
